lyrics:
Verse:
Under the neon lights, we move, Tokyo's calling, in this groove,
Exploring streets, where samurais once roamed,
In Kyoto's temples, where peace is home,
Mount Fuji's shadow, in the sunrise glow,
Sakura dances, as the cool winds blow (whoosh) Chorus:
Vámonos, hermano, to the land of the rising sun,
Singing bajo la luna, our adventure has just begun,
From the hustle of Shibuya to the calm of Nara's deer,
This journey with you, brother, brings the world so near.
